---
title: Roasted Vegetable Paella with Garlic Aioli
description: Want to take your taste buds on a trip to Spain, no passport required? We’ve got just the thing. This iconic dish has warm and smoky flavors guaranteed to spice up dinnertime. In it, you’ll find tender strips of bell pepper, roasted tomato rounds, sweet peas, and tons of aromatics. For a dynamic finish, the dish is topped with lemony garlic aioli and chopped fresh parsley. No need to build a fire in the backyard or run out to buy any fancy one-use pans for this one: pure paella bliss is just 45 minutes away. Now all you need is a pitcher of Sangria...
